    • Method Detail

      • visit

        public boolean visit()
        Description copied from class: Visitor.VisitorWithPath
        Similar to Visitor.visit(WorkflowBean) - but called for every node, even if it can have children.

        The current node is available in Visitor.VisitorWithPath.getCurrentNode().

        Specified by:
        visit in class Visitor.VisitorWithPath
        Returns:
        true if this node's children should be visited. (return value is ignored for nodes which can't have children)
